name: Inazuma Eleven Strikers 2012 Xtreme
overview: Inazuma Eleven Strikers 2012 Xtreme (イナズマイレブン ストライカーズ 2012 エクストリーム, Inazuma Irebun Strikers 2012 Ekusutorīmu) is a role-playing video game and sports video game for the Wii developed and published by Level-5. It was released on December 22, 2011 in Japan.
